        "MOFFEIN_PILOT_BODY_SECONDARY_ALT_NAME": "Bombae Emissae!",
        "MOFFEIN_PILOT_BODY_SECONDARY_ALT_DESCRIPTION": "Arma tua in <style=cIsDamage>iaculator granatarum energiae</style> muta quod pro <style=cIsDamage>480% damno</style> facit. Dum <style=cIsUtility>volans</style>, pro <style=cIsDamage>3x220% damno</style> facit. Usque ad 2 tenere potes.",
